sense.gloss: having no choice but to ..., all one can do is ..., there's nothing to do except ...
having nothing but ..., there is only ..., having only ..., having no more than ...

sdata.j: ↑好↑↓す↓きになった↑人↑↓ひと↓のことをもっとよく↑知↑↓し↓りたくなったら，↑監禁↑↓かんきん↓して↑解剖↑↓かいぼう↓してみる|しか↑無↑↓な↓い|んですよ。
sdata.e: If you want to know a person you like better, you have to confine them and dissect them.
